## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for governance.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers governance visibility,
decision/review-aware display,
escalation state,
historical governance reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- governance context must resolve
- decision/review scope must resolve
- accountability scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid governance context
- invalid role separation
- invalid escalation path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish decision state,
review state,
escalation state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- governance runtime scope is explicit
- role-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
